content.detailedDescription: I was approaching my front lawn from a walk, and my eyes were drawn to a bright, white, circular orb in the sky about 75-80 degrees from horizontal in the east-southeast direction. the orb was about ten times larger than the largest star or planet reflection i've seen and about a hundred times smaller than the moon.  it was about the size of a green traffic light (light only) from about 5-6 car lengths away. the clearly-defined orb grew in size very slightly, but rapidly, with fuzzy edges, like an ever so slight fuzzy edge burst, then it seemed to suck the light back in or collapse inward and was gone.  thinking it was fantastic, i looked at my android to record the time, then i sat outside on the driveway for about ten minutes looking upward for a return performance, or any sign of a plane in flight, or anything to explain what i saw. i noticed the area in which i saw the orb was in the vicinity of a small cluster of stars whose name i do not know.  obviously it wasn't as far away as the star cluster, but the small constellation was a landmark that i noticed while i was sitting there.  i only saw the orb for a second or two and got no pictures, so i'm sure this will be marked as "insufficient data," or might be a common phenomenon associated with something explainable, but i wanted to report it just in case any other people had a similar experience and had more evidence than i.
content.summary: Bright, white, dime-sized orb grew in size then collapsed and disappeared

content.detailedDescription:
- iowa mufon asd, beverly trout, is submitting this telephoned report.  sighting date is november 4, 2015, between 5:00 and 6:00 a.M. - probably closer to 6:00 a.M., and this witness would have been seeing objects very likely at the beginning of nautical (mid) twilight before dawn  (sun rose at 6:50 a.M. on 11/4/2015.)

witness was lying awake in her indoor hammock looking through west-facing window when she saw two silent objects moving (very fast) n to s at about 10 degrees elevation above/beyond a treeline some ¼ to ½  mile land distance.  sun was not yet risen; it was near the beginning of mid-twilight before sunrise.  she could see lots of stars, and found herself wondering about two objects that were quickly moving from n to s.  “what is that?” she wondered.  “why does it seem like ‘twinkles’ through the bare tree branches and on over to a treeline some ¼ to ½ mile distant?”
bright, lighted (or reflected light) round (disc) form was following behind, at a slightly higher altitude, a lower, dark, oval shaped  object.  as witness watched, the upper, lighted object seemed to “catch up” to the lower, dark object.  with one directly above the other, the two objects seemed to stop/hover, very briefly, then the lower, dark object emitted a lengthy fiery flame out its rear (like an ascending rocket).  witness describes flame as 1.25 degrees in length in a somewhat rectangular shape, in other words, it did not seem to narrow down or “tail off” at the rear of the flame. dark object seemed to then separate slightly from the flame, and begin a slanted ascent as if to continue on south.  at separation, flame persisted for perhaps 2 more seconds before disappearing.  however, at this point, both objects simply blinked out.  duration of sighting is estimated at 8 seconds, or less.   witness comments that objects seemed “far off,” yet thinks they were not very far away, and admits that she has problems in spatial perception.

experimenting with 10 degrees, at various land distances ranging from 1 to 3 miles, and using ¼ full moon (.125 degrees) yields various possible actual sizes ranging from 23 to 35 feet in diameter.  these guesstimates re land distance may be way off, and the witness could only offer an apparent size estimate of the objects as bigger than a bright planet.  she compares the objects’ size to airliner climb-outs during take-offs from the airport some 2 miles land distance.
content.flightPath: Path with directional change,Path then hovering
content.summary: Two objects, one brighter, higher & behind the other, n to s.  lower dark object emitted flame, separated from flame, headed at angle, then both blinked out/disappeared.

content.summary: Moved across the sky at a very high rate of speed. perfectly horizontal

content.detailedDescription: At 5:11pm saturday, 7th of september, i was driving my car on the way to the supermarket in victoria , gozo , when i looked directly up in the sky just above the road, something caught my attention. i saw 3 objects that were in a triangular pattern, they seemed to reflect light, they were almost silverish in color, but the bottom one looked a bit orange. they were shaped what looked like a long oval shape but each one was  stationary at a 45 degree angle. as i stopped the car to watch this phenomena , i realized the two shapes at the top of this triangular pattern were fading, and at the same time, the bottom shape of this triangular formation was moving ( i really cannot state how fast, but if they were large objects, as they seemed to be, the bottoms one must have been moving quite fast, perhaps as fast or faster than a modern airplane) and continued to a north western direction, toward cloud-cover, at which point i had lost track of the object, but not before taking photos, with my  mobile phone camera, ( which are not very clear, but you can definitely see a pattern in the sky if you look closely)
content.summary: 3 strange reflective shapes in sky, in a triangular formation, the top two shapes disintegrated into the atmosphere over time as the bottom shape moved in a north western direction

content.detailedDescription: I was asleep in my bed, i did not know what was going on until i realized they have taken my conscious mind through what could only be explained as a tunnel. i did not witness the exterior, but i seen the interior. it looked to be roughly 25 feet from wall to wall, in a circular shape with a large blue crystal behind the being speaking to me. this being spoke through telepathic means, explaining that i was chosen to be given a new body once my current body expires. i was shown this new body that they built for me, it was an exact physical replica of me, but they said that it would far surpass any and all other human beings on earth. they explained that the body has been enhanced through genetic manipulation, making the bones extremely dense, improving my muscular system which in turn would increase my speed, strength, and endurance. they then explained that my new mind would also be enhanced, allowing me to use the mind's full capacity. the new body was floating in what i could only describe as a cloning tube, but i cannot be positive.

content.detailedDescription: I went outside on the morning of october 23, 2015 at 3:30am to smoke a cigarette because i was unable to sleep. i observed a bright object that looked like one of the closer planets to earth in our solar system. i thought this at first because the object was stationary for a short period of time, was extremely bright and appeared to change color like some of the closer planets appear to do in the night sky. when i got half way done smoking my cigarette i began to notice the object was moving at a extreme rate of speed, doing maneuvers that no man made aircraft can do. at this time i actually slapped myself in the face because i did not believe what i was whitnessing. i quickly grabbed my iphone and began recording the ufo. i immeadiatly yelled to my girlfriend who was asleep to come outside and make sure i was not losing my mind. she soon verified the object was moving at a very high rate of speed in every direction and was just as amazed as i was. the object continued to move erraticly for the two hours that i stayed outside. the object would do the most extreme and most awkward maneuvers. it almost looked as if it were teleporting through the sky; doing loops, going back and fourth, up and down moving in all directions (north,south,east,west) very quickly. the object would all the sudden appear to hover stationary and then quickly begin doing these same awkward maneuvers. the object appeared to be flashing random colors of red, white, blue and green during the whole sighting. i am a u.S. army veteran and deployed to afghanistan in support of operation enduring freedom (oef) 2012-2013. during my deployment and my four years of service, i never witnessed any military or civilian aircraft that could move anything like this ufo. i was in one of the army's elite combat avaition brigades (cab) and was stationed on many different airfields all around the world that had the army's and air forces most elite aircraft. with that being said, i've witnessed every aircraft that our military has to offer in the night sky and nothing comes even close to how this ufo moved in the sky. i have about a five minute video of the ufo and i'm glad to share it with the public and to mufon. the video was shot on my iphone 6 and the quality is not that great. i had to zoom all the way in to see the ufo on my camera phone. i really wish that i had a top of the line video camera available to record this, but all i had at the time was my iphone. thank you for your time!
content.flightPath: Stationary,Hovering then path,Straight-line path,Path with directional change,Path then hovering
content.summary: I observed a bright, flashing object that appeared stationary at first, then "bounced" in every direction, then hovered again. not from this planet

content.detailedDescription: I was at home north of stephenville, tx in my front yard looking at stars. i thought it was a satellite at first because it was northeast of me moving towards southeast and looked much higher than a plane. barely visible at first unless you had good eyes. but then it stopped and was completely stationary. it looked just like a star. i watched it for a minute or two and then it started moving erratically. it seemed to do figure eights and half circles before reversing back around another half circle. sometimes it seemed to fade out completely and sometimes it seemed much closer to me. it did not flash at any point, just once that i saw it went out for a couple of seconds and then came back on. i watched it for at least 15 minutes, and a storm was rolling in to the north east. it rained for a while but after the clouds cleared i went back out about an hour later and the thing was still there! stil behaving the same. eventually i had to go to bed because i had to work today, but the thing was still moving around to the south east when i went to bed. i was able to show it to my wife and also to my mother. i was fascinated by this as i often stargaze and had seldom seen anything this interesting.
content.summary: Thought it was a star at first but then it started moving

content.detailedDescription: I started meditating about a week ago, learning to try to project my thoughts etc.. tonight i decided to sit outside and project my thought and see if they would reveal themselves. about half an hour into me staring up i kept repeating please show me. i was looking straight up leaning against the rails on my deck when it just happened. a bright blue object entered my vision from the left. surprisingly close and bright.. sooo bright! it came in slow out of no where. it moved in a straight line, slow like a helicopter, then it just shot off faster than anything i have ever seen. if i hadn't of been looking up at that specific spot in the sky at the right time i would have mistaken it for a shooting star. it had no tail no lights it made no sound. i cannot even believe what i saw. it made me cry. they are real! the closest thing i have seen to my sighting was nasa footage where it shows them coming in and then shooting off. what i saw tonight was amazing.
content.summary: I asked them to show themselves and they did by lighting up directly above me and then shooting off...

content.detailedDescription: I was walking my dog just before 8:00 pm in our residential neighborhood. i was facing south when i saw a bright white object move steadily across the sky just above trees in the near distance. it moved from east to west and appeared to be descending slightly. it moved in a straight line for maybe three seconds before it was out of view. this object was closer than an airplane flying in the area. it did not blink or flash but was solid with no additional lights. i only saw light, no solid object around it. i do not think it was a falling star or meteorite, it had no tail or streak. the only other thing it could be is a drone with a bright led light on it. this was over a neighborhood park, and as we approached it i thought maybe i would see someone but no one was there. this was on the west side of madison, wi.
content.summary: Madison, wi solid bright white object moving east to west low on horizon. no blinking, no tail, no sound.

content.detailedDescription:
Hi, okay this is a bit different.  i didn't see a ufo, i seen a hole in the sky or something that would make it look like there was a hole in the sky.  i know that sounds strange but it's true.  

i was living in racine and driving my daughter and her friend to a store in waukegan, il... it was a gorgeous day, the sky was a beautiful blue yet i was a bit irritated because the sun started to glare off cars and i forgot my favorite sun glasses.  so i had to wear the only pair that i had, peach ones that i'd left in the glove box.  i never liked them because i have high cheek bones and they cut into my cheeks but i wore them anyway.

so we're on hwy 31 going about 50 mph just passing kenosha and getting to the border when i looked up and saw a very large oval shape, it was way up there and within it was a very dark blue background.  it looked as if there was a hole in the sky, a perfect hole of oval shape. 

the best way to describe it is how it looks like when you get a hole in your pantyhose and you see the skin.  

i looked away at other parts of the sky which were normal and then looked back and yep, it was still there.  it was way up and it must have been huge... i'd say 3 football stadiums across and was actually very scary as it did seem like someone had ripped a hole in the atmosphere and whatever it was was beyond that.

thinking i might be going crazy i took my glasses off and gave them to my daughter.  i asked her to put them on and tell me what she sees...  she did and it took a few moments but she finally looked in the direction where i'd seen the strange phenonenom and said, "i see a hole in the sky".

what's really weird is i was thinking about it the other day and tried to find those glasses but now they are gone and i don't know where they went... but still i know it happened... 

i'd never seen it before that and haven't seen it since.   i will admit i've had a couple strange things happen to me... i'm a survivor of some very horrible child abuse and sometimes i think there's someone (or something) who does watch over me.  i have pictures of orbs which i could sense in my apartment (which i'm sending to you) and once i had an orb the size of a quarter come right at me and then disappear, leaving me with this amazing feeling of unconditional love.  i tried to get into same mindset to have them come to me again but that hasn't happened since either.  

but i have to admit the hole in the sky was about the scariest thing i've ever seen...  you can call me and i'll talk to you if you need.  thanks...

- lisa swanson
content.summary: Hole in the sky

content.summary: I was testing my new nikon p900 taking pictures of the moon. i didn't see anything until i developed the film and saw what seems to be ufo's orbiting close to the moon.
